#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The style that follows your style. The style selected here is used when "
"starting a new paragraph by pressing <keycap function=\"enter\"></keycap>. "
"This is useful, for example, for headlines, after which you usually want to "
"start a normal paragraph of text."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenu
#: apps_librewriter.xml:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inherit From"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apps_librewriter.xml:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A style that your style depends on. If the selected style is changed, your "
"style changes as well. For example, to make headers consistent, create a "
"<quote>parent</quote> header style and have subsequent headers depend on it. "
"This is useful when you only want to change the properties that need to be "
"different."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apps_librewriter.xml:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For details about the style options available in any tab, click the "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> button of the dialog."
msgstr ""

